{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Physics Based</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ball is really rolling. Even if you're not pressing the buttons, it might be still in motion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Energy System</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll decide how high the ball jumps, but you need to decide before it jumps. Timing is crucial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/Energy.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dash/Slow-mo Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When aiming, time slows down and you use the energy to push the ball. Use this for your advantage and last-minute rescues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/Slowmo.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Power Ups</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your maximum energy increases when you collect power-ups, and some other parameters improve with more energy. You'll become stronger overall. Try not to miss these things because you may need to jump over bigger gaps in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/Powerups.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Floating Objects</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are some objects floating in the air. They probably won't stay in place when you land on them. It's good to be careful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/FloatingObjects.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enemies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are little tentacles hanging around. At first glance they don't seem to do much, but they won't leave you easily and if they are around you long enough you will die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/Enemy.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Some Puzzle Elements</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some doors are locked, and you'll need to find the buttons to open them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/Puzzle.gif?t=1736276872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Checkpoints</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a checkpoint system, but obviously you have to reach the checkpoint first. Good luck.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/3d439f8324330ea8e52b8960ec2d92cbca4e9d1e.jpg"},{"name":"Harder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/19f187ada21da69817e672e16518dba18010f9c4.jpg"},{"name":"Stronger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/f32be975bd38c5cd0be9fdcc76cfc7636380d1bb.jpg"},{"name":"Most Important Button Of The Game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/ccc4f361dd84ee20153516aa8adc7e74f4e53647.jpg"},{"name":"Strike","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/b4f38f2b0bf20f36ce5583109b52601a13a3406b.jpg"},{"name":"Faster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3026830/0abd397188002f5879374df2449ace78fc169eea.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.